name: Purging UL RF old messages
command: [select * from MTFMSG_DELV where insdte < DATEADD(HOUR, -4, GETDATE()) and rcvflg = 1 order by moddte desc]|[delete from MTFMSG_DELV where msg_id = @msg_id and mod_usr_id = @mod_usr_id and wh_id = @wh_id]|[delete from mtfmsg where msg_id = @msg_id and mod_usr_id = @mod_usr_id];
